229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9759506514308217, \"rank\": 0.024272194090882163, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans have the added confidence of two recent wins over Serbia, in a pre-Games friendly and in group stage play, but coach Steve Kerr cautioned they could not afford to relax.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 488, \"end\": 501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3096209165917631e-15, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999939625720698, \"rank\": 5.677799374294806e-06, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Kerr\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Serbia is really good,\\\" Kerr said.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999939625720698, \"rank\": 5.677799374294806e-06, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We can not get lulled to sleep because we beat them twice.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have to be prepared for their best effort.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got to think about, what are they going to do differently,\\\" Kerr added.\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every game is so different and unique.\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You never know when the ball's going in, when it's not going in.\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have to be prepared.\\\"\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the Americans' triumphant progress so far, James insisted that any team still standing - France will face Germany in the other semi-final - is a threat.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2826313009079866e-14, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.945241212293048, \"rank\": 0.05793101501936611, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.995647340525533, \"rank\": 0.0043716879422247825, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everybody, everybody, everybody,\\\" James said when asked to name the most dangerous team remaining.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2826313009079866e-14, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"James, the NBA's all-time leading scorer, leads a US Olympic team more stacked with star-power than any since Michael Jordan's 1992 Dream Team.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2826313009079866e-14, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.047957361831748e-18, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour