ce\": \"It brings the best out of you.\\\"\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was certainly the case for France, who had to eke out an overtime win over Japan and were comprehensively beaten by Germany in group play.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2365, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.945241212293048, \"rank\": 0.05793101501936611, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2413, \"end\": 2418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9986426061844078, \"rank\": 0.0013008235311369706, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2454, \"end\": 2461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.995647340525533, \"rank\": 0.0043716879422247825, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They looked like another team as they booked a semi-final rematch with reigning World Cup champions Germany with an 82-73 victory over previously unbeaten Canada.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2578, \"end\": 2585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.995647340525533, \"rank\": 0.0043716879422247825, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\